      <title>真主党使用光纤无人机攻击以色列目标</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/world/middleeast/hezbollah-fiber-optic-drones.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩武装组织正在使用由光纤电缆控制的爆炸性无人机攻击以色列军队，就像乌克兰战争中常用的无人机一样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/world/middleeast/hezbollah-fiber-optic-drones.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 21:10:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院判决后，路易斯安那州考虑重新绘制房屋地图</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/louisiana-suspend-primaries-supreme-court.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路易斯安那州国务卿表示，在法院裁定该州国会选区违宪后，众议院初选将被推迟。参议院初选将于5月16日进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/louisiana-suspend-primaries-supreme-court.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 20:38:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院投票权裁决可能会推动选区重新划分战争的新时代</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/supreme-courts-voting-rights-gerrymandering.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计将出现的新国会地图可能会导致竞争性选区减少、选民向民选官员问责的方式减少以及政治更加两极分化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/supreme-courts-voting-rights-gerrymandering.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 19:56:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格斯称伊朗停火已停止等待国会批准</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/hegseth-iran-cease-fire-congress.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长在战争结束 60 天前夕作证，这是总统撤军或寻求国会批准继续战斗的重要法定期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/hegseth-iran-cease-fire-congress.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 19:14:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在撤回凯西意味着提名后任命妮可·萨菲尔为卫生局局长</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/casey-means-surgeon-general-withdraw.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[米恩斯博士的提名陷入停滞，部分原因是她对疫苗的看法。总统表示，他转而提名纪念斯隆凯特琳癌症中心的放射科医生妮可·B·萨菲尔 (Nicole B. Saphier) 博士。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/casey-means-surgeon-general-withdraw.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 18:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗最高领袖表示计划维持对霍尔木兹海峡的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/world/middleeast/iran-war-supreme-leader-mojtaba-khamenei-strait-hormuz.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿亚图拉哈梅内伊在一份声明中表示，伊朗将为霍尔木兹海峡建立“新的法律框架”。他还表示，他的国家将保留其核能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/world/middleeast/iran-war-supreme-leader-mojtaba-khamenei-strait-hormuz.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 16:41:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票权决定如何阻碍年轻黑人领袖的崛起</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/voting-rights-act-young-black-democrats.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南方的黑人民主党人在寻求政治职位时已经面临严峻的挑战。但最高法院的裁决可能会影响一代人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/voting-rights-act-young-black-democrats.html</guid>
