    <item>
      <title>特朗普的伊朗封锁如何让高风险的中国之行变得复杂化</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/trump-china-iran.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果特朗普总统按计划于五月飞往中国，那么首要话题显然将是一场北京已明确表示其认为没有必要的战争所产生的连锁反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/trump-china-iran.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 16:23:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>农作物少计引发人们对美国农业部可靠性的质疑数据</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/business/usda-farmers-crops-data.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年玉米种植面积预计减少了 450 万英亩。农业部表示，导致这一失误的原因是缺乏调查回应，而不是裁员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/business/usda-farmers-crops-data.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 15:22:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
